Sum, Kicking, Phone
You are just getting deeper into your work, but suddenly getting disturbed by the loud giggling of your colleagues?
Unintentionally listening to a phone call that you better not have heard?
One should not annoy colleagues with buzzing, singing, loud conversations (which one conducts over their heads), cramping, constant scolding or nodling.
